snippet.title: Against the Storm: Keepers of the Stone - Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Rebuild from the ruins with Frogs, the expert stonemasons and waterworkers, and send Striders on lucrative expeditions in the new Coastal Grove biome.

Against the Storm: Keepers of the Stone expansion pack launches on September 26th, 2024!

Add to wishlist: 
• STEAM: https://store.steampowered.com/app/3075500/Against_the_Storm__Keepers_of_the_Stone/
• EPIC GAMES STORE: https://store.epicgames.com/p/against-the-storm--keepers-of-the-stone
• GOG: https://www.gog.com/game/against_the_storm_keepers_of_the_stone
• MICROSOFT STORE: https://www.microsoft.com/p/against-the-storm-keepers-of-the-stone/9nt8j0wpnxqt

Join our community:
• YouTube: https://www.youtube.com/c/EremiteGames/
• Discord: https://discord.gg/against-the-storm
• Reddit: https://www.reddit.com/r/Against_the_Storm/
• X/Twitter: https://x.com/ats_citybuilder
• Twitch: https://www.twitch.tv/eremitegames
• Hooded Horse: https://linktr.ee/hoodedhorse
• Eremite Games: https://linktr.ee/against_the_storm

Voice-over narrator: Eli Harris
